{"tid":1676586,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"義氣博義氣 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-26T14:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:18:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9bd02f562fe09538097de0c1fc618d770bb16e","tid":1676586,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191026/20793864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191026%2F20793864%2F&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=dbaf1531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191026%2F20793864%2F&h=68979af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191026/20793864/</a><br />\n<br />\n義氣博義氣 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191026/large/1571994852_f87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191026%2Flarge%2F1571994852_f87b.jpg&h=cb98ca32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逆權抗暴運動至今，示威持續，送中惡法撤回、罪魁禍首林鄭面臨撤換、跋扈殺人黑警面臨報應&hellip;&hellip;社會因一人之私一隊之惡，撕裂分化，無法回頭。<br />\n<br />\n網民將食店劃分為愛港（義助過學生的）黃店，親共（撐警及辱罵過示威者的）藍店、中立（有爭議性但不明顯）綠店，編輯詳盡清單，二千多間食店分佈圖一覽無遺，製作精美又用心，供港人隨己意挑選。<br />\n<br />\n18區充斥催淚煙山埃顆粒殘留物，我咽喉不適咳嗽，抵抗力弱，後遺症很多，近日吃素，清粥小菜及滋潤湯水也未癒──想起前線年輕人所受傷痛，除了中毒煙還被捕被虐打被殺害，心痛。黃藍店清單我未必適用，但有一家以後一定會呼朋引類去「懲罰」的。<br />\n<br />\n龍門冰室5家分店支持反送中，向學生提供免費餐，日前一對母女來黐餐，但理念不同曲解張老闆原意，與其他食客爭執，張要求藍絲離開了事。24號其紅磡分店遭5漢掃場刑毀，消息一出，「瞓身」逼爆餐廳的食客湧至，以義氣、行動和感激回報，張生損失約十萬元，自問沒做錯，不打算報警，他不信警察，認為要查也要查721為先。<br />\n<br />\n食客根本不介意沒冷氣一地狼藉，如流水不斷。那些爆裂的玻璃，其實也是一道風景，建議他留一兩塊不用更新，作為抗爭歷程「紀念」。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"43cfd57f1ddb2bebb03f68ca41d1631c3fd9ddc1","tid":1676586,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:18:13.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d5c9be693f249f89d3350cf22970847ba7ae9e","tid":1676586,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxQS8O3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxQS8O3.jpg&h=96d43958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rrj8G84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrj8G84.jpg&h=f1b77f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wrmGhHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwrmGhHq.jpg&h=8eba718d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vY9rAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vY9rAM.gif&h=72303cc9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}